{"version":1,"content":"<html>\n  <body>\n    <p>您是否曾夢想過閱讀速度能提升三倍，並能更深入地理解內容呢？Speed Reading Learn 3x Faster 這款強大的閱讀訓練 App，能為您量身打造個人化的學習旅程，讓您在更短的時間內吸收更多資訊，無論是學生、專業人士或是熱愛學習的終身學習者，都能透過它顯著提升閱讀效率與記憶力，現在正是您免費獲得終生版升級的最佳時機。</p>\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/460x460bb-75-8.webp\" alt=\"限時免費\">\n    <h2>全方位科學化閱讀訓練</h2>\n    <p>Speed Reading Learn 3x Faster 採用經科學驗證的方法，提供個人化學習路徑，幫助使用者從基礎到進階，有效提升閱讀速度、專注力與理解力，透過有趣的遊戲化練習，例如舒爾茨表格訓練，它還能強化周邊視覺和記憶技巧，讓學習過程不再枯燥乏味，進步軌跡清晰可見。</p>\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/1242x2688bb-10-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/1242x2688bb-11-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/1242x2688bb-12-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/1242x2688bb-13-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/1242x2688bb-14-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/1242x2688bb-15-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <h2>限時免費領取終生版</h2>\n    <p>Speed Readingo Read 3x Faster 終生版內購限時免費中，用戶完成初始化後看到收費牆，Lifetime 價格顯示為$0 即可免費收下。</p>\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/IMG_9919-473x1024.webp\" alt=\"IMG 9919\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/IMG_9920-473x1024.webp\" alt=\"IMG 9920\">\n    <ul>\n      <li>應用名稱：Speed Reading Learn 3x Faster</li>\n      <li>應用類別：Education</li>\n      <li>下載位置：App Store</li>\n    </ul>\n  </body>\n</html>","scraped_at":"2026-05-01T20:51:34.960994+00:00","quality":{"score":1,"chars":470,"images":9,"source":"New MobileLife","fallback":"none"}}